Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream: Ah! See? New posters!\NWe never had those underwater!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't keep you in\Nsuspense any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're bringing one of\NPonyville's oldest traditions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to our school!\NThe Fetlock Fete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The what-lock-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pony dance party!\NThey're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to\Ndo that, Ocellus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This year, the\Nevent's at school
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and open to everycreature.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're calling our\Ndance the "Amity Ball".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona not know\N"Amity Ball" dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona only know traditional\Ndance of Yakyakistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ball dance like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly. It isn't\Njust one dance;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a whole night of 'em!\NPlus an awesome party!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll have all the old\NFetlock Fete traditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pony-Pal contest,\Nthe Lucky Pot Dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So like this says, "Get your\NPony-Pal and come along!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go? I got\Nnothing better to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You had me at "Dinner."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who wants to help\Nme hang more posters?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Yona, want to\Nbe my Pony-Pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We can enter the\Ncontest together...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yona yak.\NYona not pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pony. Pony. More Pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, that's just a poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, it'll be tons of\Nfun together! Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Yona go with Sandbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! I'll get the\Ntickets. See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha !
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona not let Sandbar down!\NYak best at being Pony-pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yona not sure\Nhow if she not pony...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Terribly sorry, Yona.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All these dresses I'm\Nsewing for the dance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,have me completely frazzled!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dress? Yona need\Ndress for dance!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona have lots to learn\Nabout being best Pony-Pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[sewing machine humming]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[knock at door]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona interrupting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ha ha! Well, not\Ninterrupting exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,More like blocking the flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,stopping me from what I'm doing..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yes, interrupting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... what can I\Ndo for you, Yona?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona not know yak need\Nspecial pony dress for dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona no can wear what\NYona always wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona could. I\Nmean, you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Fetlock Fete,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever\NTwilight is calling it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it's all about a tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain way to do\Neverything at the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That what\NYona want to learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How to do all the Pony things.\NEven if Yona has to wear dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, er.. if that's\Nwhat you really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm! Yona be best\NPony-pal for Sandbar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, at an elegant\Naffair like a Pony dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,one must converse in a\Nsophisticated fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking with Brussels\Nsprouts in your mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,helps you learn to {\i1}articulate{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a mouthful and\Nrepeat after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"How kind of you\Nto ask me to tea!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"May I offer you\Na glass of punch?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"The weather is quite\Nagreeable today."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona like Brussels sprouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We will need to do something\Nabout your hair style,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but first, let's\Nfind the right dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...purple taffeta,\Nfrosted chiffon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] gold brocade,\None of my favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona like brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Blech. Earth tones. They're so... heh..\Nearthy, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry; we\Nshall find something
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to make you stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona not want to stand\Nout. Yona want to fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Quite. And by the\Ntime we're through,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be like you've\Nbeen going to pony dances
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The more you know{\i0}\N{\i1} how things are done, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ the more confident{\i0}\N{\i1} you'll be. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ There's more to a dance{\i0}\N{\i1} than just having fun ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And there's no better{\i0}\N{\i1} teacher than meeeeeeeee ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Rarity! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Yona see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ When I'm finished with you,{\i0}\N{\i1} you'll start to fit right in. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Listen to me when I say: ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Once you learn{\i0}\N{\i1} the pony way, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ you'll start to{\i0}\N{\i1} fit right in. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ No need to wait another day. ♪ {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ To be part of our smart soiree. ♪ {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The perfect dress. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ A color all the{\i0}\N{\i1} rage but still unique ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Now lose the braids ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Try a style more{\i0}\N{\i1} fantastique. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Here's what we'll do, ♪{\i0}\N{\i1} ♪ A horn-icure and a de-frizz ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We'll try shampoo ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ What ever yak part this is. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Too curly{\i0}\N{\i1} Too blue ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Too retro{\i0}\N{\i1} Too new. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Too Twilight{\i0}\N{\i1} Too furry. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We'll find one.{\i0}\N{\i1} Don't you worry ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Choose what you want{\i0}\N{\i1} to be and be it! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Picture a you to{\i0}\N{\i1} see and see it. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I'm the mare to guarantee{\i0}\N{\i1} it, you'll fit right in. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ My plan, my grand design, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Your friends will{\i0}\N{\i1} thrill to find ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ A new you that's{\i0}\N{\i1} too divine ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah you're gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Fit right in. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Right in! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Listen to me when I say, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Once you learn{\i0}\N{\i1} the Pony way. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You'll start to...{\i0}\N{\i1} Fit right in! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Yak not waste another day{\i0}\N{\i1} to be part of your Pony waaaaay! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Yak not waste{\i0}\N{\i1} another day to ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Fit! Right! In! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I almost forgot! The most\Nimportant part of the Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yona already\Nhave Pony-Pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh not that, darling.\NThe DANCING!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know precisely\Nwho can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Rainbow Dash and\NFluttershy good at dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so surprised! I'm\Nawesome at EVERYTHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for baking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two traditional dances
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that everypony does at the Fete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,After a few days of\Npracticing with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll know them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And fit right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely. We'll start\Nwith the slow dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the Pony Cotillion. That's\NFluttershy's specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, heh, I wouldn't say\Nspecialty; it's just fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Yona. I made you a chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is\Nfollow these dance steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll learn\Nthem in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now. Just start walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Step on whatever color\NI name. Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue. Red. Step ahead\NGreen, black, now step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue. Red. Step...Oop.\NNo. Yona start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue, red,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Green, black...\NYak step back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Black, green, red and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Red, black, hold one and two...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Red. Blue. Red\Nonce more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Green black blue\Nred three and four!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona feel like she\Nhave four front feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.. Um, maybe we should\Ntry this again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Yona!\NThat was the hard one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's WAY easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A little dance called\Nthe "Pony-Prance."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The key to this one is SPEED!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Yona! Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get with the flow\Nand let yourself GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona LIKE to flow and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Sweet\NApple Acres, Yona!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity tells us\Nya need some help
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,getting ready for\Nthe big dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,SOME! Ha! Indeed. And we only\Nhave a few more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've come\Nto the right place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you ask me what my\Nfavorite part of the dance is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say everything about the\Ndance, but especially...this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fetlock Lucky\NPot Dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of the\NPonyville dance tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony brings\Na dish to share,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and we swap 'em without\Nknowin' whose is whose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Although my Lucky Pot\Nprobably gives me away. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cook\Nanything you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But can I suggest... oh, I\Ndon't know maybe.. CUPCAKES!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Er. I already told Yona a little\Nbit about that tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's even brought her\Nown Lucky... bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak buckets are best buckets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona think make\Ntraditional Yak dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tree Root Stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Extra fiber! Mmm!\NPonies like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. I'm not sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just in case,\Nlet's get baking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Flour, milk, sugar,\Nbutter icing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we mix and we beat\Nand we pour into pans
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and we bake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And now YOU try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Achoooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's one way to mix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try something\Na little simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can do\Nsomething with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Applesauce it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue...red...green...blue....!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[muffled] How kind of you\Nto ask me to tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[slowly] How kind of you\Nto ask me to tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue. Red. Step ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How kind of you. Green,\Nblack, Yona step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...to ask Yona to tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Black, green, red and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Red, black, hold one and two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Red. Blue. Red once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Green black blue\Nred three and four!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! She's dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout that?\NAnd she's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona! If someone at the party\Ntells you they're thirsty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you say...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,May Yona, um, may {\i1}I{\i0}\Noffer you a cup of punch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By Celestia, I\Nthink she's got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You dance great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And are so well-spoken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be the hit of the Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You've mastered{\i0}\N{\i1} so many pony ways ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And grown a lot in{\i0}\N{\i1} the past few days ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You've shown a turn that{\i0}\N{\i1} has earned our praise ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And now I{\i0}\N{\i1} Fit Right Iiiiiin! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You Fit Right In! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everycreature! I'm\Nyour DJ Scales N' Tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,spinning your favorite\Ntunes all night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So welcome to the Fetlock\NFe--I mean, the Amity Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad I'm\Nhere with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I'm not the only\Nnon-pony in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not still worried\Nabout that, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Headmare Twilight said,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dance\Nfor everycreature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no\N"pony pressure."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have\Ntold Yona that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Our teachers have been helping\Nher get ready for the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been taking lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone full\Npony for the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For me? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How kind of you to ask me\Nto this soiree, Sandbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah..!\NEr..\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You look\Nso... weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona..?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite. Oh, I do hope I make\Na good pony-pal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.. Of course you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yona, you didn't need\Nto do any of...this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are you\Ntalking so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not talking\Nfunny. I'm fitting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Could've fooled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona! You look absolutely\Nscrumptious, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I get that for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a\NLucky Pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely like ponies prepare!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, everycreature\Nto our school's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,first annual Amity Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For those of you who've never\Nattended a Fetlock Fete,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't wait to show you\Nsome of our fun traditions
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,on this special night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So Spike...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Er. Scales N' Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right. Scales N' Tail.\NLet's get this party started!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, party ponies! It's\Ntime to raise the roof
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and stomp your hoof for the\Ntraditional first dance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of the night...the\NPony Cotillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Yona know this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! Green, black,\Nthen step back. Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hee hee!\N[chuckle]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! How did you learn this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I had good teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona never practice\Ndance with dress on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. I mean... heh, heh, may I offer\Nyou a cup of punch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Time to shake\Nthings up a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, everycreature,\Nit's the Pony Prance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.. maybe we should\Nsit this one out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I do so LOVE\Nthe Pony Prance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK, Yona!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop bouncing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wig...come...OFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What a calamitous Yakciddent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Yona not all right!\NYona want to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona sad. Yona sing\Nsad song. Sad Yona.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona no blame bird. Yona no\Nwant to be around Yona either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona sad, Yona sing sad song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How Sandbar find Yona?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you pretty well by now.\NI figured you'd come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's\Nwhere I'd go
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if something like\Nthat happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar mean something\Nawful and embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So awful, Yona cannot come\Ndown from treehouse ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Sandbar bring\NYona food and water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it really\Nwasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anycreature\Nhardly even noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe one\Nor two didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If they happened to be in\NCanterlot for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, it's\Nall over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, will you come back\Nto the dance with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona disappoint Sandbar. Yona\Nnot make very good pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you think\Nyou disappointed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And who said anything about\Nhaving to be a good pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona just want to do all\Nthe right pony things
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and fit in at dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe Sandbar and Yona\Nwin Best Pony-pals Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, Yona win\NWorst Pony Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Sandbar name two\Nponies worse than Yona.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy Glow and Sombra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. OK. Sandbar right.\NThey worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona, it doesn't really\Nmatter if you're a great pony
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or a horrible pony. You're\Nthe best YONA I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I asked\Nyou to the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted you\Nto be anything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,other than\Nwhat you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend,\NYona. The Yak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you say? Let's\Ngo back to the dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NI'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We ALL are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie: Yona, are\Nyou all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We were so worried when\Nyou disappeared like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:20:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona fine. But Yona sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not mean to make such a mess\Nand ruin the pony dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Sugarcube.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, WE\Nshould be apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were\Njust teaching you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,how to have fun at the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We never meant to try to turn\Nyou into something you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend help Yona feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: And that's why we're\Ngiving you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! The Pony-Pal Prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, it's the\NAnnual Amity Ball Award
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No pony-ness required.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We all decided that you and\NYona totally earned this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your actions tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,exemplified the true\Nmeaning of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona! I'm glad you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony wants to learn\Nthat crazy dance you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak-Dance? Is easy. Yona teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If everycreature\Nwant to learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked for it and\NDJ Scales N' Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is gonna deliver!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everycreature join Yona for...\Nthe Yakyakistan Stomp!
